title: Tennis has "significant" integrity problems, admits report
text:
Tennis has "significant" integrity problems, admits report Thursday, April 26, 2018 - 01:09
Independent Review of Integrity in Tennis announces the extent of 'integrity problems' in the sport are 'serious and substantial'.
